  <brief_title>The Objective is to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Masitinib in Combination With Riluzole in the Treatment of Patients Suffering From Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group, Phase 2/3 Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Masitinib</official_title>
  <sponsors>
